Package edu.rit.mp.test

Package edu.rit.mp contains unit test programs for package edu.rit.mp.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
Buf01 Class Buf01 provides an integer buffer for the Send01 and Receive01 programs.
Receive01 Class Receive01 is a main program that receives MP messages from the Send01 program.
Receive02 Class Receive02 is a main program that receives MP messages from the Send02 program.
Receive03 Class Receive03 is a main program that receives MP messages from the Send03 program.
Send01 Class Send01 is a main program that sends MP messages to the Receive01 program.
Send02 Class Send02 is a main program that sends an MP message to the Receive02 program.
Send03 Class Send03 is a main program that sends MP messages to the Receive03 program.
Test01 Class Test01 is a unit test main program that creates and accepts channel connections in the Message Protocol (MP).
Test02 Class Test02 is a main program that sends and receives MP messages using the loopback channel.
 

Package edu.rit.mp.test Description

Package edu.rit.mp contains unit test programs for package edu.rit.mp.
